            <h2>Quick Overview</h2>
            <p>GemCrest is a professional-grade billing and inventory management solution designed exclusively for
                jewelry businesses in India. It combines powerful features with an intuitive interface to help you
                manage your shop efficiently.</p>

            <h3>Key Features</h3>
            <ul>
                <li><strong>GST-Compliant Invoicing:</strong> Generate professional invoices with all tax calculations
                    handled automatically</li>
                <li><strong>Inventory Management:</strong> Track every item with weight, purity, HUID, and stock levels
                </li>
                <li><strong>Customer CRM:</strong> Maintain customer profiles with purchase history</li>
                <li><strong>Metal Rates:</strong> Update daily gold/silver rates for accurate pricing</li>
                <li><strong>100% Offline:</strong> All data stays on your device, no internet required</li>
            </ul>

